headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Import/Export Coming December
content:
Import/Export introduces a whole new series of criminal pursuits as CEOs & their organizations boost, modify & resell the most wanted vehicles for big profits. It will take talent, coordination & the tactical use of new Special Vehicles to get the job done.

New Vehicle Warehouses will house the results of your operations & you'll be able to add massive Executive Office Garages with up to three floors of storage for as many as 60 vehicles.

Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
